---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Outreach" description="Public engagement: the Hannah Arendt Institute, public lectures, the PACT School Tour, and media appearances.">

  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Outreach</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        As a publicly funded researcher, I believe research should serve the broader society. Through public lectures, school visits, media engagement, 
        and my work with the Hannah Arendt Institute, I try to make academic knowledge about polarisation and democracy accessible and actionable.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HAI -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px; padding: 2rem;">
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          <img src="/images/hai-logo.png" alt="Hannah Arendt Instituut" style="height: 50px; width: auto;" />
          <p class="section__label" style="margin-bottom: 0;">Hannah Arendt Instituut</p>
          </div>
        <h2 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Senior academic fellow</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.75; max-width: 720px; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          The <a href="https://hannah-arendt.institute/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hannah Arendt Institute</a> for diversity, urbanity, and citizenship is a collaboration between VUB and UAntwerpen, based in Mechelen. It bridges scientific knowledge about citizenship, urban life, and diversity with the practices and insights of policymakers, organisations, and citizens.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.75; max-width: 720px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          As a member of the <a href="https://hannah-arendt.institute/samenwerken/onderzoeker/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">academic team</a>, I help organise academic and public events, bring expertise on polarisation and democratic resilience to the Institute, and contribute to programmes like <strong style="font-weight: 500;">PolarProf</strong> that support local governments in addressing harmful polarisation, disinformation, and hate speech. I am proud to be part of this fantastic organisation.
        </p>
        <a href="https://hannah-arendt.institute/project/democratie-en-polarisatie/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="section__more">View my HAI profile →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PUBLIC TALKS -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px; padding: 2rem;">
        <p class="section__label" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Public engagement</p>
        <h2 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Public talks</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.75; max-width: 720px; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          I regularly give public lectures, panel discussions, and school visits on polarisation, democracy, and critical thinking. I speak to a wide range of audiences: secondary school students, university classes, local governments, civil society organisations, media professionals, and the general public.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.75; max-width: 720px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          Highlights include guest lectures for the <a href="https://www.vub.be/nl/nieuws/vub-pact-school-tour-caroline-pauwels-atheneum-polarisatie" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VUB PACT School Tour</a> (Caroline Pauwels Academy of Critical Thinking), presentations at public events via the Hannah Arendt Institute, and the <a href="https://checkfirst.network/event/lunch-lecture-with-kamil-bernaerts/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">EDMO BELUX Lunch Lecture</a> on polarisation. Interested in inviting me for a lecture, debate, or workshop? <a href="/contact/">Get in touch</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- IN THE MEDIA -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section__label">In the media</p>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; max-width: 680px;">
        My research on institutional design, polarisation, and democracy has been covered in Belgian and international media.
      </p>

      <div class="pub-item">
        <div>
          <p class="pub-title">Onderzoek VUB: Belgische democratie minder gevoelig voor polarisering</p>
          <p class="pub-authors"><a href="https://www.knack.be/nieuws/belgie/politiek/onderzoek-vub-belgische-democratie-minder-gevoelig-voor-polarisering/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Knack</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-meta"><p class="pub-year">2022</p></div>
      </div>

      <div class="pub-item">
        <div>
          <p class="pub-title">VUB: Belgische democratie is minder gevoelig aan polarisering</p>
          <p class="pub-authors"><a href="https://www.hln.be/binnenland/vub-belgische-democratie-is-minder-gevoelig-aan-polarisering~a19058f5/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Het Laatste Nieuws</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-meta"><p class="pub-year">2022</p></div>
      </div>

      <div class="pub-item">
        <div>
          <p class="pub-title">Notre système politique belge divise moins la société en deux</p>
          <p class="pub-authors"><a href="https://www.rtbf.be/article/notre-systeme-politique-belge-divise-moins-la-societe-en-deux-que-les-democraties-majoritaires-selon-une-these-de-la-vub-11120434" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RTBF</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-meta"><p class="pub-year">2022</p></div>
      </div>

      <div class="pub-item">
        <div>
          <p class="pub-title">Onderzoek VUB: Belgische democratie minder gevoelig voor polarisering</p>
          <p class="pub-authors"><a href="https://www.bruzz.be/samenleving/onderzoek-vub-belgische-democratie-minder-gevoelig-voor-polarisering-2022-12-09" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BRUZZ</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-meta"><p class="pub-year">2022</p></div>
      </div>

      <div class="pub-item">
        <div>
          <p class="pub-title">La démocratie belge moins sensible à la polarisation</p>
          <p class="pub-authors"><a href="https://www.lalibre.be/belgique/societe/2022/12/09/la-democratie-belge-moins-sensible-a-la-polarisation-MQ7FYPXDKVFLJO7TVFDED2L3QA/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">La Libre Belgique</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-meta"><p class="pub-year">2022</p></div>
      </div>

      <div class="pub-item">
        <div>
          <p class="pub-title">Belgium's democracy less prone to polarisation</p>
          <p class="pub-authors"><a href="https://www.brusselstimes.com/politics/335217/belgiums-democracy-less-prone-to-polarisation" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Brussels Times</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-meta"><p class="pub-year">2022</p></div>
      </div>

      <div class="pub-item">
        <div>
          <p class="pub-title">La démocratie belge moins sensible à la polarisation</p>
          <p class="pub-authors"><a href="https://www.rtl.be/info/belgique/politique/la-democratie-belge-moins-sensible-a-la-polarisation-1420273.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RTL Info</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-meta"><p class="pub-year">2022</p></div>
      </div>

      <div class="pub-item">
        <div>
          <p class="pub-title">"Democracy is never finished" — interview with Kamil Bernaerts &amp; Didier Caluwaerts</p>
          <p class="pub-authors"><a href="https://www.vub.be/en/news/democracy-is-never-finished" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VUB News</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-meta"><p class="pub-year">2024</p></div>
      </div>

      <div class="pub-item">
        <div>
          <p class="pub-title">Polarisatie: bedreiging of motor voor democratie? — press release PhD</p>
          <p class="pub-authors"><a href="https://press.vub.ac.be/polarisatie-bedreiging-of-motor-voor-democratie" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VUB Press</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-meta"><p class="pub-year">2025</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PHOTO -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <img src="/images/public-speaking.jpg" alt="Kamil Bernaerts giving a public lecture" style="width: 100%; max-width: 800px; border-radius: 4px;" />
      <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-text-faint); margin-top: 0.5rem;">&copy; Greetje Van Buggenhout</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
